Subject: Digital Armaments July-August Hacking Challange: Microsoft


Challenge Publication is 06.15.2006
http://www.digitalarmaments.com/challange200606483923.html

I. Details

Digital Armaments officially announce the launch of July-August hacking challenge. 

The challenge starts on July 1. For the July-August Challenge, Digital Armaments will give 5000 credits EXTRA for each vulnerability submission that results in the publication of an Microsoft advisory.

The submission must be sent during the April month and be received by midnight EST on August 31, 2006. The 5000 credits prizes will be given on the publication of a official Microsoft Bullettin with severity High regarding the vulnerability. The 5000 credits will be an extra added to the normal vulnerability payment (check the DACP scheme).

 

II. References 

